Fmoad Cailin
============

Partial reimplementation of FMOD with OpenAL.

Once a great stronghold, now much of it stands in ruins.

Similar project: https://github.com/moon-chilled/openfmod

What You Need
-------------

* fsb-extract-dumb
* python-fsb5 with extract.py (fsb5-extract module on OpenBSD)
* manifest files
* json-c
* ...

How To Use
----------

... under construction ...

JSON Files
----------

* find basename with jq:

```
$ jq '.events[] | select(.path == "event:/char/madeline/jump") | .files[] | .filename' path/to/file.json
$ # => returns "char_mad_jump"
```
* prepend name of the database:
```
$ jq '.path' path/to/file.json
$ # => returns ""bank:/sfx"
```
* construct the final path with directories and extension:
```
./Content/FMOD/Desktop/sfx.banko/sfx-char_mad_jump.ogg
```

